884
00:38:35,190 --> 00:38:35,840
Oh, by the way,

885
00:38:36,320 --> 00:38:37,360
the other day,

886
00:38:37,910 --> 00:38:39,150
I went to the Teachers' Office at night

887
00:38:39,600 --> 00:38:40,670
