967
00:42:37,710 --> 00:42:38,390
Mr. Liangji,

968
00:42:40,040 --> 00:42:40,870
I heard...

969
00:42:42,560 --> 00:42:43,950
I heard that

970
00:42:44,120 --> 00:42:46,080
Magistrate Xie gave two hectares of land

971
00:42:46,080 --> 00:42:47,000
